br />\n都係你隻寵物黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗"},{"pid":"9ce2de88aeb52139ac06bb6356122abf3057e59c","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想佢死後流浪</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得放係屋企，起碼個地方佢都熟悉d"},{"pid":"a76ce90938098f33263559a61784eb97108a0bb0","tid":441282,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"我阿媽都反對放喺屋企，但我會堅持擺喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申：寶貝仔啱啱歲半，唔想佢大得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e433099282b9140e2fa4c5a2b9844e50b5eb651","tid":441282,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻狗仔岩岩過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下巴打你地係放屋企定灑左佢？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺屋企，搵個盒仔裝住佢，唔想佢再流浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺spca領的黑貓女...."},{"pid":"af0570743c10d6f36db6a4912288d35dadb427f5","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我阿媽都反對放喺屋企，但我會堅持擺喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申：寶貝仔啱啱歲半，唔想佢大得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再養過???<br />\n我真係唔敢再養,我好多年都無喊過<br />\n但佢走左之後3,4日我都KEEP住一諗起佢就喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66719a00939fa5cc1c45a1d98d39e83aaf34cb8","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻狗仔岩岩過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下巴打你地係放屋企定灑左佢？？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擺屋企，搵個盒仔裝住佢，唔想佢再流浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺spca領的黑貓女....</blockquote><br />\n依家放左係屋企,死都堅持唔灑左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f891e84c28086fb756c59ec065a63e1272392a2","tid":441282,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"我放入間房到"},{"pid":"c846905b721651d017cee93933941fc80b49c5b8","tid":441282,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"唔係鬼唔鬼既問題<br />\n係冇位擺"},{"pid":"79a32a31a0cc5e6de98d63f1026901b518a0822b","tid":441282,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我阿媽都反對放喺屋企，但我會堅持擺喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申：寶貝仔啱啱歲半，唔想佢大得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再養過???<br />\n我真係唔敢再養,我好多年都無喊過<br />\n但佢走左之後3,4日我都KEEP住一諗起佢就喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我諗我都會繼續養，仲有好多狗等緊人畀個家佢，之但係未必再養呢種品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264c6b63f89f2f9668c0318cb96768c01cba5231","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T18:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係鬼唔鬼既問題<br />\n係冇位擺</blockquote><br />\n個骨灰龕好細姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a423feab4cfe095311243565d0c07026c70a89","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T18:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我阿媽都反對放喺屋企，但我會堅持擺喺屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申：寶貝仔啱啱歲半，唔想佢大得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再養過???<br />\n我真係唔敢再養,我好多年都無喊過<br />\n但佢走左之後3,4日我都KEEP住一諗起佢就喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我諗我都會繼續養，仲有好多狗等緊人畀個家佢，之但係未必再養呢種品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係無膽再養<br />\n一黎好怕再傷多次<br />\n二黎真係唔係好多時間可以陪住佢<br />\n好好彩佢最尾個半個月我咁岩辭左職可以長時間陪佢,唔係我一定會好後悔"},{"pid":"1b170bfcc1c70fcd517e91d5a642815198de10c5","tid":441282,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"當可立克沖咗黎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4e094bddfb9b306f062d429471a769b77a7d0c","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當可立克沖咗黎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我祝你快d有可立克飲"},{"pid":"aa1dba07783e2d6f674b3dfd83647cb518e064ef","tid":441282,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"擺屋企,等我死左同我擺埋一齊"},{"pid":"af03f0cedd19941223ea204de1ce82422ebd5534","tid":441282,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"第時你父母百年歸老又擺係屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9895875c153c17a3e6ac33fe78fb64f52b6dc2","tid":441282,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:53:26.000Z","msg":"沖水飲"},{"pid":"10e98cfc673ed7f91e5e89cf2976c19cdfe93548","tid":441282,"uid":52020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第時你父母百年歸老又擺係屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第時先算喇<br />\n可能遲D好多人都慣左放屋企,本身都唔信依D野擺屋企真係無所謂"}]}